title: Godfather Run
description:
There are two sides to every issue: one side is right and the other is wrong, but the middle is always evil. - Ayn Rand

Jason loaned his friend Chris some money which he borrowed from a shady individual named Minji. Today he must pay it back with interest, but due to some new information, Minji's interest changes. 

Cast: Steven Ramirez, Nancy Chung, Jalila Bell, Cherry Fu, Yun Xioa, Danielle Baskerville, Irene Elle and Ashleigh Whitfield.
